00:00:02,376 --> 00:00:05,072
difference between syntax and semantics.

3
00:00:05,133 --> 00:00:08,880
The syntax deals with the sets of formulas themselves. It is

4
00:00:08,980 --> 00:00:12,791
a mechanical process which could be carried out by a machine.

5
00:00:12,933 --> 00:00:16,710
The semantics deals with the interpretation of these symbols

6
00:00:16,810 --> 00:00:19,554
and is where our intuition lies. Here we can

7
00:00:19,654 --> 00:00:22,785
