27
00:01:33,733 --> 00:01:37,024
then we can show that indeed Sigma models phi, since

28
00:01:37,124 --> 00:01:41,785
all possible transitive and irreflexive structure are also assymetic. So,

29
00:01:41,885 --> 00:01:45,698
we have two different worlds, the mechanical world of syntax

30
00:01:45,798 --> 00:01:49,219
and the intuitive world of semantics. It is natural to

31
00:01:49,319 --> 00:01:52,415
